@section HO-020
title: State Transitions
summary: Keep FE and BE state interpretation aligned
links: FE-STATE-001
content:
<<<
[State transitions]
1) idle -> loading
2) loading -> success
3) loading -> fail
4) fail -> loading

[Exception handling]
- retryable true:
- retryable false:
>>>

